data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!!! Welcome to your spacious oasis! Enjoy one-level living in this 5-bedroom, 2-bath ranch-style home offering the perfect blend of comfort and style, with an open concept design that's perfect for modern living & creates an inviting space for family gatherings and entertaining. Kitchen features an island and extra dry-bar space which provides extra counter space & storage.  Primary bathroom features a double vanity, shower and tub combo and separate toilet area.  Out back you will find a covered patio and fully fenced backyard provides a private area to relax & enjoy fresh air!  2-car attached garage provides space for parking out of the heat or extra storage space! Roof replaced in 2021!  This is a must see!  Make your appointment for a private showing today!
